  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Calcified NCC

          -  Perilesional edema on CT or MRI

          -  Normal lab values

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Viable neurocysticercosis

          -  Status epilepticus

          -  Symptomatic intracranial hypertension

          -  Tuberculosis

          -  More than 7 days after seizure

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
